Package: bcaddressgeocoder
Title: Interface to the BC Batch Geocoder Service
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stephanie", "Yurchak", , "Stephanie.Yurchak@gov.bc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Province of British Columbia", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Provides a simple interface to the BC Batch Geocoder
  web service for submitting batch geocoding jobs, monitoring their
  status, and downloading completed results. Based on the python code,
  github.com/bcgov/ols-devkit/blob/gh-pages/als/batch_address_list_submitter_py3_3.py,
  and translated with the help of AI.
